S.FORM: == kakaliman == Yi-ta-li ta-paw-ciw 義大利大堡礁 Ta-paw-ciw " igu : Great Barrier Reef" u satabakiay satanayuay nu kitakid a San-hu-ciw subal, itida i tip tay-pin-yen a Aw-cuo wali amis dadipasan nu bayu, tanayu namaka Aw-cuo wali amis Kun-se-lan-cuo hekalay a San-hu bayuan, amis namaka Tuo-lei-se bayuan, nutipan katukuh Nan-huy-kuy-sin nu timulan "timul nu laa'tan 10ﾟtimul nu laa'tan 24ﾟ",satanayu sa ku ahebal makaala tu tulimsepsep kun-li, ahebal caylimcay kuli. .
